\i0 \cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs55\fsmilli27648 \cf2 \cb3 Always be on the lookout for companies that are moving toward the formation of a network effect. If they can be found and purchased at bargain prices, investors have real opportunities to earn significant long-term rates of return.}